{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179220/extras/steamdesc1.png?t=1701705657\" /><br><br><strong>Around Us</strong> is a 2d prop hunt party game centered around the childhood game \u201cHide And Seek/Prophunt\u201d. <br>Originally designed for 5-8 players you can play anywhere from 2-8!<br><br><strong>There are over 100+ props to choose from and hide as,</strong> that are randomized each time you play, <br><br><strong>8+ engaging tasks to complete</strong>, including memory games, puzzles, and more!<br><br><strong>Everyone is included!</strong> while playing, you will never have a dull moment, it is enjoyable no matter what role you get!<br><br><strong>You can play among or around your friends!</strong> players are randomly selected to be a hunter or a hider, <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179220/extras/steamdesc4.png?t=1701705657\" /><br><br>Hunters main objective is to find the hiders or props and eliminate them, <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179220/extras/steamdesc5.png?t=1701705657\" /><br><br>And the hiders main objective is to finish their tasks without being caught with switching between props and hiding.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179220/extras/steamdesc6.png?t=1701705657\" /><br><br>You can select how many hunters you would like, and how many tasks the hiders need to complete.<br><br>And If you do not have any friends, you can  join random lobbys, meet new people, and make more friends.<br><br><strong>Get ready to cure your boredom and party with around us</strong>, and Wishlist the game today!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"100 PROP CHANGES","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2179220/7a8f0c7c3bbee7229bc76165